articles.author: Christian Edwards
articles.title: Moldova backs joining EU by razor-thin margin as president condemns ‘assault’ on democracy - CNN
articles.description: Moldovans have voted by the thinnest of margins in favor of joining the European Union, near-complete results showed Monday, as President Maia Sandu condemned an “unprecedented assault” by foreign actors on the country’s democracy.
